name: sajou manaka/沙条愛歌(Fate/Prototype)
description:
This lora was based on the model anythingv4.5 and trained by picture of the sajou manaka in Fate/Prototype, there are many problems in the first attempt, which may be improve after being skilled. It is recommended that the weight be around 0.8 with tag:sajoumanaka,1 girl at the front of the prompt may be better at least that's what I tested.

2023.4.25

Update the new version sajoumanakaV2.0

2023.5.22

Update the new version sajoumanakaV3.0
